        public void initialize(java.net.URL location,

        Abstract method of the interface Initializable. Starts the thread that administrates the loading of the highscore counter. Sets the event for pressing the "Start Playing" button for changing the view from highscore screen to start screen. Sets the event for pressing the "Quit" button for ending the game.

        initialize in interface javafx.fxml.Initializable
